---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import LinkButton from "../components/LinkButton.astro";
import PatreonButton from "../components/PatreonButton.astro";
---

<Page title="Support Us" description="Support Us">
  <main>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-sans">Support Us</h1>
    <div class="mt-3 mb-6 border-b-subfooter border-lsq-orange w-24"></div>
    <p class="mb-2">LSQ is volunteer-run and we depend on your purchases and donations to pay our authors and keep the site running. Help support women writers and consider pitching in!</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-normal font-sans mb-1">Join the community</h2>
    <PatreonButton />
    <p class="mb-2">For as little as a dollar a month, you can become part of this amazing community of writers. We have rewards for those that pledge a little more. ðŸ™‚</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-normal font-sans mb-1">You can also:</h2>
    <!-- TODO: Insert https://buymeacoffee.com/lunastation button here -->
      <table>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td><LinkButton url="/find-issues" linkText="Purchase" /></td>
                <td>Take LSQ with you everywhere! Your purchase goes directly towards paying our authors and keeping the site running.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><LinkButton url="https://weightlessbooks.com/luna-station-quarterly-12-month-subscription/" linkText="Subscribe" /></td>
                <td>Get a yearly subscription via Weightless books is a great way to keep new issues coming every quarter.</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-normal font-sans mb-1">Spread the word!</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 mb-2">Tweeting, Tumblring, and generally sharing a link to LSQ is a huge help to us in spreading the word about the great stories and awesome women writers we feature here. Following us gets us more reach and exposure, too!</p>
      <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-center space-x-5">
        <LinkButton url="https://www.twitter.com/lunaquarterly" linkText="Twitter"/>
        <LinkButton url="https://www.facebook.com/lunastnquarterly/" linkText="Facebook" />
        <LinkButton url="http://lunastationquarterly.tumblr.com/" linkText="Tumblr" />
        <LinkButton url="https://wandering.shop/@lunastation" linkText="Mastodon" />
        <LinkButton url="https://bsky.app/profile/lunastation.bsky.social" linkText="Bluesky" />
      </div>
    </main>
</Page>